---
title: Mumbai Yoghurt Chicken & Garlic Rice with Cucumber Salad & Cashews
description: There’s nothing better than chicken that’s juicy on the inside and wonderfully charred with mild Mumbai-style spices on the
outside. That’s how we’re preparing our dinner tonight, plus add a dollop of creamy yoghurt to double down on all that flavour.
